{"tid":530180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以自己尿液頂包代釋囚驗毒判囚　懲教員提司法覆核圖保退休金","createTime":"2018-01-15T13:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T01:32:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b76c84a0ed25409d1d97b871503ed726bd23d705","tid":530180,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:43:53.000Z","msg":"兩名懲教人員2009年無依程序探訪戒毒釋囚，更用自己尿液頂包送檢，再填假報告呈交上級，令釋囚通過監管。兩人承認公職人員行為失當罪，判囚3個月。其中前一級懲教助理梁肇榮今日入稟高等法院提司法覆核，要求法庭頒令終止取消退休金程序。<br />\n<br />\n申請人梁肇榮，答辯人為懲教署長林國良、公務員事務局長羅智光，及行政長官林鄭月娥。申請人在入稟狀中要求法庭頒令永久終止「取消本人退休金的程序」，宣告署長聲稱其行為失當罪行核證並無法律效力，惟入稟狀未有透露其他詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180115/s00001/1516009228151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180115%2Fs00001%2F1516009228151&d=HW7sH8%2FlW9AFzI22btbTk9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0719b6ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180115%2Fs00001%2F1516009228151&h=128bda85\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180115/s00001/1516009228151</a>"},{"pid":"16243a933302aac2d4aec16dae1b3146c102c9f1","tid":530180,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:47:48.000Z","msg":"祝佢早日生癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593a912fdacb82a3b3fa910bcdae38372e9cd483","tid":530180,"uid":39601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"犯左法仲想納稅人養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c976af143bd33fc3ec30be9fa4ebed7b15c632e9","tid":530180,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:32:03.000Z","msg":"打撚到佢上終審"}]}